        void transform(E element,
               Ranking ranking,

        Transforms the given element based on the provided ranking parameters.

        The ranking object contains the min and max value so the ranked value can be calculated.

        Parameters:
        element - element to transform
        ranking - ranking configuration
        interpolator - interpolator
        value - element's value for this ranking
